<br>
I don't mean to flame, but I frankly grow tired of proposals for wholesale revamping of EQ.  Let's not fall prey to the illusion that VI is listening and cares.<br>
<br>
The game is in its last stages.  Let them fix as much as they can and enjoy it before we move on to something else.<br>
